# Epics Overview

## Epic 0: Authentication & User Management (Phase 2)
Multi-platform authentication system with SSO, biometric auth, and session management.

## Epic 1: Receipt Capture & Processing
Core receipt capture functionality with OCR, batch processing, and retry mechanisms.

## Epic 2: Receipt Management
CRUD operations, categorization, search, filtering, and notes management.

## Epic 3: Export & Integration
Export to accounting formats (QuickBooks, Xero), API integrations, and webhook support.

## Epic 4: Analytics & Reporting
Dashboard, spending insights, category analysis, and trend reporting.

## Epic 5: Settings & Administration
User preferences, app configuration, data management, and admin tools.
